{"tid":620490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成廿幾卅歲人先信星座，男人老狗，會唔會好on9","createTime":"2018-04-07T15:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T15:36:38.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a99e380771d1ee40976110fd2c0b54f412b82e10","tid":620490,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"因為自己有好多性格上、際遇上既野唔識解釋<br />\n成日俾人話我點點點<br />\n好想改變，但改極都係面個浸，自己心知根本唔係呢種人<br />\n但睇返星座<br />\n一路睇一路覺得係喎，就係咁喇，點解連我自己都唔識用文字形容既野，人地網上三兩句就解釋得咁透澈？！<br />\n不過都係玩下算，得個知字算"},{"pid":"ddcfcd1380c49c98297ca863321c44dfa152c3c3","tid":620490,"uid":103615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"關性別咩事？"},{"pid":"6c761ade68993d84bf66e6b3012382ce34a5c9cc","tid":620490,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"天蠍？"},{"pid":"ba716fc8d45dae2ae6f439eb4deca2afe4901876","tid":620490,"uid":34773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:28:21.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寫星座條友真係收錢作文咁作<br />\n補堆template 改， 字眼重重覆覆一樣"},{"pid":"6d32a70e1be23220568ad62ef6ca35f4708d120f","tid":620490,"uid":129704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"On9先信星座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}